Well, if you're here, I guess I should say something about myself, so uh... ...Hi? Well, anyway, hello! My name is Nate and I am 18 years old. I live in Southern California in the U.S. I love Minecraft PVP and MCZone and I live for the thrill of battle! Likes: Chocolate (Except Mr. Goodbar), the color Teal, California Winter, Rain, Cameros, Coca-Cola, People who don't go out of there way to be a complete and utter d*** Dislikes: Beef, the color Orange, California Summer, Sunburn, the Common Cold, World Hunger, and People who spam chat until my head explodes If you see me, say hi or something I guess sorta lol Btw my computer is very finicky when it comes to sending friend requests. Most of the time I can send them myself but sometimes I can't; if so, then send me one instead. I haven't had trouble accepting any requests so far :) See you out on the field of battle! #RalphieRage2014
